  <h4>Configuring Multiple In-Place Editors</h4> 
  <p>It is possible to configure a component so that it has multiple in-place editors. When multiple in-place editors are configured, you can select the appropriate content and open the appropriate editor. See the <a href="../../../sites/developing/using/multiple-inplace-editors.md">Configuring Multiple In-Place Editors</a> documentation for more information.</p> 
